# Summary
This documentation details the Appfit destination integration with Amplitude, allowing users to stream events and cohorts to Appfit for mobile dashboard visualization, weekly metric reviews, and team collaboration features, requiring a Server Secret Key from Appfit and specific event selection during setup.

